18:24.602 --> 18:25.836
Aw, Maggie.

18:25.904 --> 18:28.321
Cliff, I am so ashamed.

18:28.389 --> 18:30.423
You're right.
The baby isn't yours.

18:30.442 --> 18:33.794
I just didn't know
where else to turn.

18:33.862 --> 18:35.595
Well, what happened, Maggie?

18:35.647 --> 18:37.647
Well, um, up in Canada,

18:37.715 --> 18:39.450
I met a man and fell in love.

18:39.517 --> 18:41.418
And everything was perfect,

18:41.452 --> 18:43.153
and we were gonna get married.

18:43.288 --> 18:46.223
And then he got scared
and called everything off.

18:46.290 --> 18:48.809
And I didn't have anyone
to turn to,

18:48.877 --> 18:51.695
so of course,
I thought of the most decent,

18:51.763 --> 18:53.613
honourable man I know.

18:53.682 --> 18:55.949
I'm sorry, Cliff.

18:56.000 --> 18:58.636
You know, you...

18:58.703 --> 19:01.705
