Maggie, but, uh...

19:31.903 --> 19:33.820
you know, I've always
thought the world of you.

19:33.821 --> 19:36.323
And I know that you'd
do the same for me

19:36.391 --> 19:38.858
if the situations
were reversed.

19:40.828 --> 19:42.629
But, Cliff, how could the...

19:42.696 --> 19:44.731
Never mind.

19:44.799 --> 19:47.067
All right.
So, hey, look, here's what we do.

19:47.068 --> 19:49.035
We, uh, skedaddle down
to the City Hall,

19:49.036 --> 19:51.372
