her the good news.

19:53.274 --> 19:54.641
Huh? Huh?!

19:54.709 --> 19:57.010
Okay!

19:57.011 --> 19:59.830
Oh, let me just call Jerry
and tell him he's off the hook

19:59.831 --> 20:01.699
