anymore.

20:01.766 --> 20:04.735
Uh, is it okay to use
this phone to call long distance?

20:04.803 --> 20:06.970
Oh, yeah, sure.
I do it all the time.

20:09.824 --> 20:12.226
Well, Sammy,
champagne all around.

20:12.293 --> 20:13.560
